    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Karaneko, players journey through a pixel art fantasy world in a relentless bullet hell RPG adventure. Confront and overcome formidable obstacles as you strive to return to your original realm.<br><br>You can examine objects, explore three distinct regions to uncover their mysterious histories, and interact with or battle non-player characters.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choices made in dialogue and combat can have short- or long-term effects that alter the game. Depending on the player's decisions, Karaneko offers a rich, diverse gameplay experience with elements of <strong>adventure, psychological, romance, and horror genres.</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102220/extras/f53966252b4fb2226da0918d71cf2d90.poster.avif?t=1760567545\" width=800 height=725 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102220/extras/f53966252b4fb2226da0918d71cf2d90.webm?t=1760567545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this magic-driven world, how can you survive without any magic? Will you overcome the challenges you face with your fists, through conversation, or perhaps by making friends and seeking their help?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102220/extras/3cffe96cf14cf0743710a4cc6548fb85.poster.avif?t=1760567545\" width=678 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102220/extras/3cffe96cf14cf0743710a4cc6548fb85.webm?t=1760567545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102220/extras/3cffe96cf14cf0743710a4cc6548fb85.mp4?t=1760567545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
